            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De contentionibus</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
      ¶ De contentionibus. Rubrica. 7.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/><ref>SAlomon in prouerb. c. 3</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e125">Ne contendas
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>aduersus hominem frustra.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e131"> /
            <ref>24. c.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e133">Ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>contendas cum pessimis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e140"> /
            <ref>20. c.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e142">Ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>norem homini qui se separat a contentionibus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/> /
               <ref>29. c.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e152">Uir sapiens si cum stulto contenderit si
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>ue irascatur siue rideat: non inueniet requiem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
             ¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 8.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e162">Non litiges
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>cum homine linguato: et ne strtas ignem illus lingus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/> /
               <ref>11. c.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e172">De ea re que te non molestat ne cer
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>taueris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
             ¶ <ref>Oratius in epistolis li. i. e. 19.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e182">Alter rixatur de
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>lana sepe caprina.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
             ¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus in epistola. 2. ad timotheum. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e192">Noli verbis contendere: ad nihilum enim vti
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>le est: nisi ad subuersionem audientium. Ineptas
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>et sine disciplina questiones de uita: sciens
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>quia generant lites.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e205">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
               ¶ <ref>Seneca de ira li. 2.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e209">Cum pari contendere <!--116.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="45-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>ancepes est: cum superiore furiosum: cum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>feriore sordidum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
             ¶ <ref>Lex diges. ti. de seruitu. vr praedi. l. iure communi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e227">Propter immensas cogitationes plerumque res
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>ad diuisionem peruenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e235">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
             ¶ <ref>Auctor li. de formula honeste vite. ca. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e239">Contendenti facile cede: nec iniurgia discepta
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>tionesque descendas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e247">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
             ¶ <ref>Ambrosius de officiis li. i. c. 2.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e251">Absit perti
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>nax in familiari sermone contentio: questio
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>nes enim magis excitare inanes quam vtilita
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>tis aliquid afferre solet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
             ¶ <ref>Macrobius saturnaliorum li. <unclear>2.</unclear> c. 18 exau. <!--2 or et?-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>liberii:</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e265">Nimium altercando veritas amittitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
             ¶ <ref>Cato. c. 2.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e275">Contra verbosos noli contende
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>re verbis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e282"> 
          ¶ <ref>Cato. ca. 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e284">Aduersum notum noli contendere verbis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>Lis minimis verbis: interdum maxima crescit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e292">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
             ¶ <ref>Isidorus solilo. li. 2. c. 26</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e296">Caue contentiones
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>Contentio rixas gignit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>Contentio faces odiorum accendit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Contentio pacem cordis extinguit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>Contentio concordiam rumpit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/> /
               <ref>Libro. 2. c. 43.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e312">Cede cito veritati.
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>In omni disputatione tene rationem.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
